}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "Y-S0036 REV4.1" and "2005-08-04 JACKSON" is silkscreened on the board. :The ''Cypress'' hub IC package is marked with "CY7C65640A-", "LFXC 0519", :"E 04 KOR", "CYP 620479", and a square (at the bottom). :The hub is using all ''STONE'' capacitors. The hub is presumed to have been manufactured in ''China''.
The power cord included with the device may be an ''unbranded'' :PA-213-50 (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.3A -> 5VDC 2.2A).
